IMF May Recommend Ukraine Loan to Board in 2 Weeks, Unian Says

-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 
2011-02-16T11:53:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/imf-may-recommend-ukraine-loan-to-board-in-2-weeks-unian-says.html
The  International Monetary Fund  will
continue discussing unsettled issues with Ukraine for two more
weeks before recommending to the board to allow the payment on
the third tranche of a $15.6 billion loan, the  Unian  news agency
reported, citing  Max Alier, head of the IMF office in Kiev.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net . 